## 13. Health & SPA Serving

### Health Check

```typescript
app.get('/health', async (_req, res) => {
  await AppDataSource.query('SELECT 1');
  res.json({ status: 'ok', db: 'connected', timestamp: new Date().toISOString() });
});
```

- Used for K8s liveness/readiness probes
- Returns 503 if DB is disconnected

### SPA Catch-All

```typescript
const clientDistPath = path.join(__dirname, '..', '..', '..', 'client', 'dist');
app.use(express.static(clientDistPath));
app.get('{*path}', (_req, res) => {
  res.sendFile(path.join(clientDistPath, 'index.html'));
});
```

- Static files served from client's `dist/`
- All unmatched GET routes serve `index.html` for client-side routing
- Must be AFTER all API routes and BEFORE error handler
